{"tid":1330658,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"[清三毛，救連登] 我有一計，解決 $0.3 三毛，其實唔難","createTime":"2019-07-18T15:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T14:35:33.000Z","uid":253691,"like":184,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"1cf575b94835d041c40a48fa0e6b59dad81d0ca5","tid":1330658,"uid":253691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:55:48.000Z","msg":"大家眼見 $0.3 三毛不停出 post 帶風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，除左 block 佢地 block 到手軟之外，好似乜都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，其實只要連仔做多少少，已經可以有效減少 $0.3 三毛！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">收發言權費！！！<br />\n唔貨金出唔到 post / 回 post</span></span><br />\n<br />\n睇到呢度，唔好起哂鋼住，下面會講點解，點樣實行，好處壞處，成功例子：<br />\n<br />\n<ins>點解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></ins><br />\n呢個方法係針對 0.3 三毛而制定嘅策略，只要理解佢地嘅日常，就明白<br />\n只要限制佢地出 post，佢地就唔可以帶風向，轉移話題，spin 走重點，打稻草人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">換言之係廢武功！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>實行建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></ins><br />\n舊 account：豁免<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新 account / 某 id number 以後：收 $3 (個價可以再討論)<br />\n當然我地都要做 d 特別 case<br />\n例如 (本地) 學生，無收入，只要佢地係學校 ISP 申請 account，咁當然豁免啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>好處</ins><br />\n1. 增加 $0.3 三毛成本<br />\n你估 spin 轉移視線唔撚使付出代價呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最緊要係，收費系統用外國野 e.g. visa / master / apple pay / google pay etc，變相 $0.3 三毛金主 去&quot;資助&quot;外國（某國人思維係咁諗，好似係），用咁嘅名義，增加佢地批錢難度；對佢地黎，畀錢麻煩（佢地未必有 visa / master etc <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），最終要搞一大輪先可能有開 post 權。\b最慘係開完 post 即刻畀人發現，連本都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 連仔有額外收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老老豆豆，自從連仔收起廣告，大家都拗底連仔頂唔住，好有心揾方法貨金，而家有個咁嘅方法，點會唔支持<br />\n[連仔已經差唔多成個月冇開廣告，頂唔頂得住㗎？] <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1282970/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1282970/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 提升 lihkg 質素<br />\n\b少左 $0.3 三毛污染，d post 都高質 d，唔使為拗而拗，畀人 up 2 句就 spin 走個 post 嘅重點<br />\n<br />\n<ins>壞處</ins><br />\n1. 連仔要 OT 整 payment system<br />\n2. 諗唔到<br />\n3. 真係諗唔到，不如你又講吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>從持份者角度分析</ins><br />\n1. 舊 account： 豁免貨金 Who fucking care? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 本地學生： 豁免貨金 Who fucking care? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. CD-ROM：反正我只讀不回，又唔開 post，Who fucking care ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4. 新 account (非 $0.3 三毛) 會開 post 打工仔：今時今日食飯凍飲都 +$3 ，Who fucking care ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5. $0.3 三毛：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開唔到新 account 出 post，今個月跑唔到數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁可能你地會話，都無用啦，收少少錢，其實之前已經<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">有案例可以參考</span></span>：<br />\n[有無手足發覺蘋果收3蚊後無晒三毛留言]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1287872/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1287872/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>FAQ</ins><br />\n1. 我新 account 無言論自由？<br />\n若果你覺得為言論自由，連 $3 都唔值嘅話，咁 LIHKG 對你嘅價值真係賤過地底泥，上唔上都罷。<br />\n<br />\n2. 窮J，但又想講野？<br />\n你揾到方法證明閣下唔係 $0.3 三毛，又窮 JJ 到 $3 都畀唔起，相信好多爸打絲打都肯幫你畀埋一份<br />\n<br />\n老老豆豆，連 times 都報埋 lihkg，可想而知，對手將會大舉進攻呢度。喺呢個公開論壇入面，我地係無方法去趕絕 $0.3 三毛，但係只要將佢地嘅成本增加，佢地一定唔夠我地黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">清三毛，救連登<br />\n我無野講</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958cf519d00175397ca8cafdb20e377eff554737","tid":1330658,"uid":166541,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:57:56.000Z","msg":"7.21 金鐘見<br />\n推"},{"pid":"b18f4082d1ee4528c254dc58745e0b75bb132f66","tid":1330658,"uid":166541,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:58:07.000Z","msg":"7.21 金鐘見<br />\n推"},{"pid":"c0cb279c619dc49daf384d41abb9e3dba07bed43","tid":1330658,"uid":166541,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:58:19.000Z","msg":"7.21 金鐘見<br />\n推"},{"pid":"6d1e1447b40382e75d0d9dea848c888382f1d140","tid":1330658,"uid":166541,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:58:51.000Z","msg":"7.21 金鐘見<br />\n推"},{"pid":"5e0deca026dfdaf6b82020baa3be526d7268acef","tid":1330658,"uid":166541,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:59:01.000Z","msg":"7.21 金鐘見<br />\n推"},{"pid":"65cf252b0c722fb5897be87fe6ca3887627ced1f","tid":1330658,"uid":104935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:02:15.000Z","msg":"有道理嘅"},{"pid":"0ff6a6ab2845fa1fb46c2e6d8d3ef6496eb99746","tid":1330658,"uid":269319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:02:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f68619f2a79faf2e54f123dec5d4e09049d28cce","tid":1330658,"uid":102121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:03:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"536aceea29a7c02efc65cc99c83316789b0996a0","tid":1330658,"uid":174900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:07:25.000Z","msg":"7.21 金鐘見<br />\n推"},{"pid":"12046dd5f99e08d16cad3839940329da15cdae17","tid":1330658,"uid":275189,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:08:04.000Z","msg":"我唔介意俾，可以當係基金，支持連登同其他民主運動"},{"pid":"2122e8924b34d51e496181d3c0b5785c5353a7a8","tid":1330658,"uid